page.title: 11HOME LIFE
page.content: { MONDAY ======== I wake up at 7:00 AM and when I get up I have a wash.At 7:30 AM I have my breakfast then I get dressed. I arrive at school at 8:40 AM.At 9:10 AM I have french , and at 10:50 AM I have music. Our lunch lasts 1hr 20 minutes. After lunch we have drama and science. I arrive back home at 4:05 PM. I get changed out of my school clothes into my jeans and I go down the Rec on my bike.At 6:00 PM I go in to have my dinner.After my dinner I watch the TV or go to play.At 9:00 PM I go in and watch the TV.I watch the TV until about 10:30 PM when I go to bed.
